},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"ff2ce2",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Usually 15-25 mg/d, divided into 2-3 doses (with largest dose administered in the morning)"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
